      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9SF6KY1EAQ17VRHQQAWX\">Added</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>​<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-38501\">LCD-37608</a> - Improved Security for Liferay API GraphQL Server:</strong> Increased protection against common threats in GraphQL APIs, improving our security posture and following best practices.</li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-38754\">LCD-38754</a> - Maintenance Mode for Storage Display:</strong> Temporarily placed the storage display on the Plans &amp; Usage page in maintenance mode in order to reassess and improve the overall user experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9NRE5H6PTZ9Y99PF8QQH\">Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul class=\"ak-ul\">\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-36975\">LCD-36975</a> - Removed Broken Link on the Overview and Activities Pages:</strong> Removed a link to the Deploy a Build page on the Overview and Activities pages that would cause the page to hang after clicking the link.</li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-38568\">LCD-38568</a> - Fixed Configuration Issue for ECK Search Service:</strong> Resolved an issue where the Elasticsearch configuration couldn't be changed using environment variables or updating elasticsearch.yml.</li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-38717\">LCD-38717</a> - 20 Environment Limit:</strong> Fixed an issue where attempting to create more than 20 environments in a project would cause it to fail with a 400 Bad Request response.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>"
      },
